{"tid":1341102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚元朗發生既事，一撚定要將何君堯同鄉黑綁到實一實","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:29:28.000Z","uid":278052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcffe624d6f3f3847e9b89e882a44c11aa2aea8","tid":1341102,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"有晒相，應該會有人拍到片<br />\n何君堯擺明有份計劃黑社會血洗元朗<br />\n完全揭露今晚黑警、黑社會、港共、港鐵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四權合作</span></span></strong><br />\n互相合作互相包庇<br />\n法治社會蕩然無存<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">何君堯以致全個建制派</span>必須承擔責任<br />\n勾結黑社會追打平民<br />\n罪無可恕<br />\n無任何比佢地割蓆嘅餘地"},{"pid":"df2b33784fa36f33017bf380e444545d402505e2","tid":1341102,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8450e1ed20bda432ffeca9404ac5060d324b1bb","tid":1341102,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}